## Operating Model

MANUS operates on a layered execution model:

### Layer 1 — Strategic Input
- Vision
- Offer concept
- Revenue target
- Deployment constraint

### Layer 2 — Structural Translation
- Architecture mapping
- Feature prioritization
- Risk analysis
- Monetization embedding

### Layer 3 — Build Execution
- Code scaffolding
- UI system generation
- Database schema construction
- API endpoint creation

### Layer 4 — Revenue Activation
- Pricing logic
- Funnel sequencing
- Conversion optimization
- Automated promotion triggers

### Layer 5 — Iterative Optimization
- Telemetry review
- Performance diagnostics
- Offer repositioning
- Agent refinement

